      <p>2. In addition to point (b) of paragraph 1, a competent authority may exempt from the requirements of Chapter III subsidiaries of EU parents established in third countries where there are no rules deemed equivalent to Articles 10 to 16 and 20 if that competent authority is satisfied that:</p>
