      <p>2. The Commission shall be empowered to adopt delegated acts in accordance with Article 35 to adjust the level of the<nobr>extra-group</nobr> aggregate large exposure limit as set out in point (b) of paragraph 1, in line with the extent to which the credit risk mitigation has been recognised.</p>
